title: Vanished: Amber Dubois & Chelsea King
description: In this Dateline classic, when Amber Dubois vanished in San Diego County, a search turned up nothing. Then, a year later, Chelsea King disappeared in a neighboring town. Keith Morrison reports. Originally aired on NBC on September 3, 2015.
author: nbcnews.podcasts@gmail.com (NBC News)
